  "observations": [
    "Hierarchical category tree in left sidebar with specialist counters at each node",
    "Top 2-4 feed positions are paid-promotion slots with TOP/Рекомендуем badges — ranking blended with paid-tier",
    "Specialist card is a dense composite: avatar + identity + rating + price-from + tier badge + verification + 2-3 specialization tags + CTA",
    "Discrete tier badges (Профессионал / Топ-мастер / Проверен документами) — categorical trust signal, not continuous score",
    "Sticky right-side filter panel with numeric ranges (price from/to, rating threshold), multi-select (metro), booleans (выезд, безнал)",
    "Format facet (Онлайн / Очно / Выезд) as quick toggle above other filters — high-traffic switch elevated",
    "Default sort is composite 'Оптимально' — explicit alternatives reveal that ranking is multi-factor",
    "Multi-step form wizard with progress bar for order creation (~6-8 steps)",
    "Conditional form fields per category (class for tutor, area for repair, problem for psychologist) — details step is polymorphic by categoryId",
    "Draft auto-save across wizard steps with 'Незавершённое' resume entry-point",
    "Preview step before publishing — shows mastering view of the task as persuasive confirmation",
    "Post-publish inbox-like bid feed with summary header (count, new, average price)",
    "Bid actions: write, mark interesting, reject — reject is irreversible with undo-toast affordance",
    "Specialist profile as tabbed detail (О себе / Цены / Отзывы / Портфолио / Видео) with sticky bottom CTA bar",
    "Reputation surfaced as breakdown (experience months, response-rate-within-hour %, repeat-client count) — not a single score",
    "Phone CTA gated by verification — capability depends on specialist.phoneVerified",
    "Observer (unauthenticated) can browse catalog and view profiles but cannot publish order or bid — read-only tier",
    "Moderator role operates on reviews/compliance surface, orthogonal to client/specialist flows"
  ]
}